{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>AuraSmart Home</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #a02020; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #c08080; /* Lighter shade of red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-animation {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            width: 300px;\n            height: 300px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background-color: rgba(160, 32, 32, 0.3);\n            animation: pulse 3s infinite ease-in-out;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero-animation::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 180px;\n            height: 180px;\n            background-color: rgba(192, 128, 128, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            animation: pulse 3s infinite ease-in-out 1s;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n            50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.2); opacity: 0.6; }\n            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #features {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--background-color), var(--secondary-color));\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .section-title::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -10px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(160, 32, 32, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            color: #ddd;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8rem;\n            }\n            .feature-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .section-title {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"hero-animation\"></div>\n            <h1>AuraSmart Home</h1>\n            <p>Experience the future of living, seamlessly integrated.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Intelligent Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Smart Lighting</h3>\n                    <p>Automate your lights to match your mood or schedule, saving energy and enhancing ambiance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h3>Secure Access</h3>\n                    <p>Control your home's security remotely, granting access to trusted individuals with ease.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-thermometer-half\"></i>\n                    <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                    <p>Maintain the perfect temperature year-round with smart thermostats that learn your preferences.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-volume-up\"></i>\n                    <h3>Immersive Audio</h3>\n                    <p>Fill your home with rich, synchronized sound, controlled by your voice or a tap.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <div class=\"about-text\">\n                    <h2 class=\"section-title\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Redefining Home</h2>\n                    <p>AuraSmart Home brings cutting-edge technology to your fingertips. We believe in creating living spaces that are not only smart but also intuitive and beautiful. Our systems are designed to blend seamlessly into your life, offering convenience, security, and comfort without compromise.</p>\n                    <p>Embrace a lifestyle where technology works for you, simplifying your daily routines and enriching your environment. Discover the elegance of intelligent living with AuraSmart.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"about-image\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x400/a02020/ffffff?text=AuraSmart+Living\" alt=\"Smart home visualization\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 AuraSmart Home. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle scroll animations if needed\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section');\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = '1';\n                        entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';\n                    } else {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = '0';\n                        entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';\n                    }\n                });\n            }, {\n                threshold: 0.1\n            });\n\n            sections.forEach(section => {\n                section.style.opacity = '0';\n                section.style.transition = 'opacity 1s ease-out, transform 1s ease-out';\n                section.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';\n                observer.observe(section);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}